,{\"name\":\"AI Content Creation\"},{\"name\":\"Multi-Platform Distribution\"},{\"name\":\"Performance Tracking\"},{\"name\":\"Optimization Loop\"},{\"name\":\"SaaS Development\"},{\"name\":\"Marketing Automation\"},{\"name\":\"CRM & Sales\"}]},\"height\":700} View Agent at Work | AI Docs Solo Founder Automation Workflow Optimization View I'll create a comprehensive workflow optimization system for your complex multi-channel business operations. This will be a detailed tactical document with visual workflows, automation recommendations, and AI agent instructions. Using Tool | Doc Generate Generate content before line 1, instruction: Create a comprehensive HTML document titled \"Solo Founder Automation Command Center: Complete Workflow Optimization System\" The document should include: # EXECUTIVE DASHBOARD - Business overview: 100+ SaaS projects, multi-platform content empire - Key metrics: 30+ posts/day across platforms, client work, product creation - Tool ecosystem map showing all mentioned tools organized by function # SECTION 1: MASTER WORKFLOW ARCHITECTURE Create detailed tables for each major workflow category: ## 1.1 CONTENT CREATION WORKFLOWS Table with columns: Workflow Name | Steps | Tools | Automation Platform | AI Agent Role | Expected Output | Time Savings Include workflows for: - Forbes/Business Insider/Success Magazine article writing - Image creation & storyboarding - Video generation (Sora 2) - Advertorial creation - LinkedIn daily content - YouTube content - Newsletter creation - Podcast production ## 1.2 SAAS DEVELOPMENT WORKFLOWS - EasySite.ai project management (100+ projects) - Client website creation - Testing & deployment - Maintenance automation ## 1.3 E-COMMERCE WORKFLOWS - Shopify POD management - Graphics upload to Printify/ShineOn - Pinterest automation - TikTok Shop management - Product research & creation ## 1.4 MARKETING & ADVERTISING WORKFLOWS - PPC ad creation & optimization - Offer creation (top 1% framework) - Digital product development - Affiliate marketing content - SEO optimization & tracking ## 1.5 SOCIAL MEDIA AUTOMATION - 30+ posts per day system - Multi-platform scheduling - Engagement tracking - Viral content optimization # SECTION 2: AUTOMATION PLATFORM RECOMMENDATIONS Create comparison table with columns: Activity Category | n8n (Local) | Make.com | Winner | Rationale Analyze each workflow for: - Cost efficiency - Integration capabilities - Complexity handling - Speed requirements - Data privacy needs # SECTION 3: TOOL INTEGRATION MATRIX Create a detailed matrix showing: - Primary tool - Connected tools - Data flow direction - Automation trigger - Integration method (API/Webhook/Zapier bridge) For each tool ecosystem: **Content Creation Stack:** - Genspark → ChatGPT → Claude → Zimmwriter → Canva → Sora 2 → Katalist **Publishing Stack:** - Vista Social, Publer, Castmagic, Taja **Development Stack:** - EasySite.ai → NewOaks → Notion → Airtable **Marketing Stack:** - GoHighLevel → LaunchCar → SearchAtlas → Growify → Subscribr **E-Commerce Stack:** - Shopify → Printify/ShineOn → Canva **AI Enhancement:** - Lutra.ai, MindPal, Pickaxe, Hugging Face # SECTION 4: DETAILED TACTICAL WORKFLOWS For each major process, create step-by-step workflow tables: ## Workflow: \"30 Posts Per Day System\" | Step | Action | Tool | Input | Output | Automation Platform | AI Agent Instruction | |------|--------|------|-------|--------|---------------------|---------------------| | 1 | Generate content ideas | Genspark + ChatGPT | Trending topics, audience data | 50 content ideas | n8n | \"Analyze top performing content in [niche], generate 50 unique angles optimized for engagement\" | | 2 | Create post variations | Claude + MindPal | Content ideas | 30 complete posts | Make.com | \"Transform each idea into platform-specific posts (LinkedIn professional, TikTok casual, Twitter concise)\" | | 3 | Generate visuals | Canva + Sora 2 | Post content | Images/videos | n8n | \"Create eye-catching visuals matching brand style guide, optimize for each platform's specs\" | | 4 | Schedule distribution | Vista Social + Publer | Posts + visuals | Scheduled queue | Make.com | \"Distribute across all platforms at optimal engagement times, stagger similar content\" | | 5 | Monitor & optimize | Taja + Growify | Performance data | Optimization report | n8n | \"Track engagement, identify top performers, generate weekly optimization recommendations\" | ## Workflow: \"Forbes/Publication Article Pipeline\" [Similar detailed table] ## Workflow: \"SaaS Project Management (100+ Projects)\" [Similar detailed table] ## Workflow: \"Shopify POD Automation\" [Similar detailed table] ## Workflow: \"Top 1% Offer Creation\" [Similar detailed table] ## Workflow: \"PPC Campaign Automation\" [Similar detailed table] # SECTION 5: AI AGENT PROMPT LIBRARY Provide specific AI agent instructions for each workflow component: **Content Generation Agents:** - Publication Writing Agent - Social Med"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=13d73ede-8fcc-4896-9e9c-0f5eddbf6095","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=13d73ede-8fcc-4896-9e9c-0f5eddbf6095"}]}]}]
